==English==

===Adjective (Idiomatic?)===
'''too hot to hold'''

# A word picture to describe something transitory and temporary in nature, such that it cannot be possessed for long, much like a literal object of intense heat.
# A problem or issue that is so volatile that it injures the one attempting to solve it; see [[hot potato]].